TC#: Verify that new user can register
Steps:
    1. Go to 'http://23076.gollos.com/'
    2. In "Authorization" dropdown select "Регистрация"
    3. Put value 'newmail@mailinator.com' into 'E-mail' input
    4. Put value 'password' into "Пароль" input
    5. Put value 'password' into "Пароль (повтор)" input
    6. Unselect "Получать рассылку о новинках и акциях" checkbox
    7. Click "Отправить" button
Expected result: Profile for new user is successfully created. Check in admin panel.

